title: Rebroadcast: Dr. Jane Exclusive-Embalmer Richard Hirschman, White Fibrous Clots, Stroke Increase & Heart Attack Increase 2022
cleaned_text:

Recently Canadian ER physician, Dr. Daniel Nagase, and other doctors also reported on the adverse effects of the covid vaccines, vaccine injuries, and vaccine shedding. Since Dr. Jane broke this exclusive story last year, more people are looking for information on Pfizer shedding, Pfizer clotting cases, vaccine shedding, vaccine injuries, spike protein. and mRNA vaccine effects.
